        {
          "scid": "sn15.16:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati … pe … ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.16:1.2",
          "pli": "“na so, bhikkhave, satto sulabharūpo yo nabhātābhūtapubbo … pe … ",
          "en": "“It’s not easy to find a sentient being who in all this long time has not previously been your brother. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.16:1.3",
          "pli": "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. ",
          "en": "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.16:1.4",
          "pli": "Chaṭṭhaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
